mention.text: 12 nov 89 -- we are receiving a report right now on the situation in san salvador
the situation in various parts of the capital city

the report we have received from san salvador , where our fighters in zacamil and other neighborhoods and residential areas in the capital city are now receiving the support of the people who are fortifying themselves in neighborhoods
the cooperation of the san salvador people
a news agency report which says that early this morning , less shooting was heard because apparently each side had consolidated their position
our fighters in zacamil and other neighborhoods and residential areas in the capital city
the people who are fortifying themselves in neighborhoods
the assassins of msgr romero pay
another evidence of the government 's weakness
the gag placed on the media
comrades : keep it up , keep an open eye , keep up the high morale as you have done up to now , seek contact with the people
